Package: measr
Title: Bayesian Psychometric Measurement Using 'Stan'
Version: 0.0.0.9000
Authors@R: c(
    person(given = "W. Jake",
           family = "Thompson",
           role = c("aut", "cre"),
           email = "wjakethompson@gmail.com",
           comment = c(ORCID = "0000-0001-7339-0300")),
    person("University of Kansas", role = c("cph")),
    person("Institute of Education Sciences", role = c("fnd"))
    )
Description: Estimate diagnostic classification models (DCMs; also called
    cognitive diagnostic models [CDMs]) with 'Stan'. Automatically generate
    'Stan' code for a variety of models, estimate your model, and evaluate how
    well the model fits your data.
